<h2 class="form_title">Selecciona tu tipo de inversor</h2>

<div data-selecttitle="Elige un tipo de inversor" class="form_block boxes">
    <div class="form_block-content radio_box big_block">
        <input name="selectperson" data-relative="selectperson-input" id="input_type" type="radio" value="personafisica" data-bind="checked: typeperson">
        <label for="input_type" class="radio_box-label">
            <i class="label_icon">
                <svg width="19" height="17" viewBox="0 0 19 17" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <g stroke="#B59971" stroke-width="2.25" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd" stroke-linecap="square">
                        <path d="M2.289 9.273l4.498 5.51M6.742 14.727L17.426 1.64"></path>
                    </g>
                </svg>
            </i><i class="block_icon">
                <svg width="32" height="22" viewBox="0 0 32 22" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <g stroke="#000" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd" opacity=".8">
                        <path stroke-width="2" d="M1.001 21h29.398V1H1.001zM1.775 6.888h29.04"></path>
                        <path d="M9.276 17h4.065M4.103 17H8.17M14.448 17h4.066"></path>
                    </g>
                </svg>
            </i>
            <h4 class="title"><span>INVERSOR INDIVIDUAL CON NIF O NIE ESPAÑOL</span></h4><span>(Persona física)</span><span class="text">Selecciona esta opción si no eres una compañía o corporación y resides en España</span>
        </label>
    </div>
    <div class="form_block-content radio_box big_block">
        <input name="selectperson" data-relative="selectperson-externaltransfer" id="externaltransfer_type" type="radio" value="personajuridica" data-bind="checked: typeperson">
        <label for="externaltransfer_type" class="radio_box-label">
            <i class="label_icon">
                <svg width="19" height="17" viewBox="0 0 19 17" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <g stroke="#B59971" stroke-width="2.25" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd" stroke-linecap="square">
                        <path d="M2.289 9.273l4.498 5.51M6.742 14.727L17.426 1.64"></path>
                    </g>
                </svg>
            </i><i class="block_icon">
                <svg width="24" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 32" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <g stroke-width="2" stroke="#000" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd" opacity=".8">
                        <path d="M1.645 8.25h20.148"></path>
                        <path d="M1.395 8.25l6.755 6.848M1.395 8.25L8.15 1.4" stroke-linecap="square"></path>
                        <path d="M21.544 23.584H1.395"></path>
                        <path d="M21.793 23.584l-6.755 6.849M21.793 23.584l-6.755-6.848" stroke-linecap="square"></path>
                    </g>
                </svg>
            </i>
            <h4 class="title"><span>SOCIEDAD, CORPORACIÓN, ETC</span></h4><span>(Persona jurídica)</span><span class="text">Selecciona esta opción si quieres contratar nuestros fondos en nombre de una entidad de derecho (sociedad, corporación, fundación, etc)</span>
        </label>
    </div>
    <div class="form_block-content radio_box big_block">
        <input name="selectperson" data-relative="selectperson-input-foreign" id="foreign_type" type="radio" value="personafisicaextranjero" data-bind="checked: typeperson">
        <label for="foreign_type" class="radio_box-label">
            <i class="label_icon">
                <svg width="19" height="17" viewBox="0 0 19 17" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <g stroke="#B59971" stroke-width="2.25" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd" stroke-linecap="square">
                        <path d="M2.289 9.273l4.498 5.51M6.742 14.727L17.426 1.64"></path>
                    </g>
                </svg>
            </i><i class="block_icon">
                <svg width="32" height="22" viewBox="0 0 32 22" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <g stroke="#000" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd" opacity=".8">
                        <path stroke-width="2" d="M1.001 21h29.398V1H1.001zM1.775 6.888h29.04"></path>
                        <path d="M9.276 17h4.065M4.103 17H8.17M14.448 17h4.066"></path>
                    </g>
                </svg>
            </i>
            <h4 class="title"><span>INVERSOR INDIVIDUAL NO RESIDENTE SIN NIF ESPAÑOL</span></h4><span>(Persona física)</span><span class="text">Selecciona esta opción si no eres una compañía o corporación y no resides en España y no tienes NIF español</span>
        </label>
    </div>
</div>